  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Oblitus mortis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face mythological creatures and legends from Venezuelan folklore, explore this entire interconnected world and enjoy a game in the purest style of the <strong>Metroidvanias</strong> classics, with a cute little twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find new and different <strong>weapons</strong>, unlock secrets with each enemy you defeat, wear different <strong>hats and masks</strong> to improve your <strong>skills</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/5d95bda824852493bb3793da0e9c29e0.poster.avif?t=1747665983\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/5d95bda824852493bb3793da0e9c29e0.webm?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/5d95bda824852493bb3793da0e9c29e0.mp4?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face legendary creatures such as <strong>La Llorona</strong>, whose lament torments the forests, <strong>Dr. Knoche</strong> and his Galipán mummies, <strong>the Hachero</strong>.  Every enemy, every area, every Object is filled with folklore and mythology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/0f76aee8c53a7874146266aafd1033ea.poster.avif?t=1747665983\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/0f76aee8c53a7874146266aafd1033ea.webm?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/0f76aee8c53a7874146266aafd1033ea.mp4?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a dark world inspired by the legends and myths of Venezuela. With pixel art graphics, this game will take you to explore the most mysterious and dangerous corners of this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/07616f793fbe28f936b6e0123e4f08bc.poster.avif?t=1747665983\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/07616f793fbe28f936b6e0123e4f08bc.webm?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/07616f793fbe28f936b6e0123e4f08bc.mp4?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Oblitus mortis</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face mythological creatures and legends from Venezuelan folklore, explore this entire interconnected world and enjoy a game in the purest style of the <strong>Metroidvanias</strong> classics, with a cute little twist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find new and different <strong>weapons</strong>, unlock secrets with each enemy you defeat, wear different <strong>hats and masks</strong> to improve your <strong>skills</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/5d95bda824852493bb3793da0e9c29e0.poster.avif?t=1747665983\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/5d95bda824852493bb3793da0e9c29e0.webm?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/5d95bda824852493bb3793da0e9c29e0.mp4?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face legendary creatures such as <strong>La Llorona</strong>, whose lament torments the forests, <strong>Dr. Knoche</strong> and his Galipán mummies, <strong>the Hachero</strong>.  Every enemy, every area, every Object is filled with folklore and mythology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/0f76aee8c53a7874146266aafd1033ea.poster.avif?t=1747665983\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/0f76aee8c53a7874146266aafd1033ea.webm?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/0f76aee8c53a7874146266aafd1033ea.mp4?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a dark world inspired by the legends and myths of Venezuela. With pixel art graphics, this game will take you to explore the most mysterious and dangerous corners of this land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/07616f793fbe28f936b6e0123e4f08bc.poster.avif?t=1747665983\" width=800 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/07616f793fbe28f936b6e0123e4f08bc.webm?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3434340/extras/07616f793fbe28f936b6e0123e4f08bc.mp4?t=1747665983\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
